Indigo744:
Ok, after a lot of search I found out that it was linked to fastclick.
I used react-fastclick  to automatically attach fastclick, but it seems it is not working properly.
Since I wanted to host locally this lib, I did the following:

yarn add fastclick
Edit index.js:
```js
import FastClick from 'fastclick';

/ Setup Fastclick /
if ('addEventListener' in document) {
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function () {
        FastClick.attach(document.body);
    }, false);
}
```
And voila! It works 😃 .

